words.sense: A book is a number of pieces of paper, usually with words printed on them, which are fastened together and fixed inside a cover of stronger pape.
A car is a motor vehicle with room for a small number of passengers.
A school is a place where children are educated.
pencil is an object that you write or draw with.
A window is a space in the wall of a building or in the side of a vehicle, which has glass in it so that light can come in and you can see out.
A house is a building in which people live, usually the people belonging to one family.
mouse is a small furry animal with a long tail.
monkey is an animal with a long tail which lives in hot countries and climbs trees.
An apple is a round fruit with smooth green, yellow, or red skin and firm white flesh.
